@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_flxycm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = 0.40
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.31)) - (0.29 * (v1 + 0.71 / tmp + 0.49)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.21)))
    tmp = wp.cos((v2 * (v2 + 0.89 - tmp + 0.02)))
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v0 + 0.26) + (tmp + 0.90 + v0 + 0.45)))
    tmp = (0.39 - 0.01)
    data[tid] = v0
